      "acceptanceCriteria": "Training and inference code version-controlled in Git; unit tests cover data-loading, forward-pass, and loss computation; dependency manifest (requirements.txt) archived with model artefacts.",
      "rationale": "The neural-network training pipeline is managed under Git version control with tagged release v2.1.0. Unit-test coverage of the surrogate codebase is 84%. All third-party library versions are pinned and archived alongside the serialised model weights. These measures satisfy MRL 2 software quality requirements."
    },
