      "rationale": "The CFD solver used to generate surrogate training data has been verified against the Taylor-Green vortex and lid-driven cavity manufactured solutions. Solver verification reports are archived and referenced. The neural-network surrogate itself is not a PDE solver and therefore classical code-verification concepts are applied at the data-generation layer only, which is consistent with MRL 2 expectations."
    },
    {
