      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry. The fine mesh (12.4 M cells) yielded GCI = 2.1% relative to the medium mesh for the volume-averaged hemolysis index at the nominal operating point. All training data were generated on the fine mesh. Discretisation error is therefore bounded and acceptable at MRL 2."
    },
    {
