      "rationale": "All five COU flow-speed combinations were included in the validation experimental matrix. The test article geometry was manufactured to nominal dimensions with tolerances of ±0.05 mm, representative of the production tolerance band under evaluation. Validation activities are therefore directly relevant to the COU."
